264
00:27:59.757 --> 00:28:06.907
3.5.2.2 If you harm them, the blowback against you constitutes part of their own position-maintenance work.

265
00:28:06.907 --> 00:28:08.857
Details omitted.

266
00:28:08.857 --> 00:28:17.507
3.5.3 Converse theorem II: Requirements outside the scope of position-maintenance methods (omitted) are of secondary importance.

