308
00:32:45.917 --> 00:32:51.355
3.8.3.3 Pricing power for good houses lies with the broad populace.

309
00:32:51.355 --> 00:32:55.305
Pro-cyclical operation yields 10% returns.

310
00:32:55.305 --> 00:33:02.292
